snippet.title: Skykipelago – Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1980460/Skykipelago/

Skykipelago is a chill strategy game where you build happy little cities in the sky. Explore a variety of colorful islands, care for your buildings' happiness, evolve your buildings to help you grow, and when solid ground is no longer cool enough for you - expand onto the cliff sides.
